We  are  pleased  to  have,  this  afternoon,  two  very  knowledgeable 
witnesses.  First,  the  Chairman  of  the  Federal  Communications 
Commission,  the  Honorable  Kevin  Martin.  And  second,  the  Acting 
Assisting Secretary of Commerce for Communications and Informa-
