with  11,000  outlets  across  the  Nation,  online,  you  know,  telephone 
operators—it’s  a  big  investment  for  them  to  be  certified.  They  had 
to  actually  put  point-of-sale  software  into  their  stores,  they  had  to 
train  their  people,  they  had  to  agree  to  be  audited,  they  have  to 
provide  NTIA  with  electronic  redemption  information,  they  had  to 
agree  to  accept  the  coupon,  and  have  the  automatic  payment  sys-
tem  from  the  Treasury.  For  them  to  voluntarily  step  up  and  par-
ticipate in this program, we are very grateful. 

Senator  CARPER.  Although  I’d  say  if  I  were  a  retailer,  maybe,  a 
